data.description: Welcome to Market 2000 Mount Vernon Dr of the Scenic Hills Subdivision in Jonesboro, Arkansas within the Jonesboro Public School District. This attractive 1729 sq ft brick and wood TRI-LEVEL home includes a 2 car garage with space for a workbench. It also has an additional door to go directly into the backyard. As you enter into this 4 bedroom, 2 bath home you will be pleased with the layout, the  large living room, and adjacent kitchen and dining area are on the main level with 3 bedrooms and a full bath on the top level. The lower level has the master bedroom which  features an electric fireplace, full bathroom and the laundry room which offers plenty of space for sorting laundry. Just beyond the dining area sliding glass door your entertaining space is extended onto the large covered deck and a level backyard. You will enjoy viewing the beautiful mature trees and listening to the calming and tranquil sounds of nature. This subdivision is just minutes from Annie Camp Junior High on W. Nettleton Avenue. Call today to schedule an appointment to see this house which could become YOUR FOREVER HOME!
